<Window xmlns="https://github.com/avaloniaui"
		xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
		xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
		xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
		mc:Ignorable="d" d:DesignWidth="500" d:DesignHeight="155"
		x:Class="SimpleBackup.InterfaceAvalonia.GettingStartedWindow"
		Title="Getting Started"
		Width="500" Height="155" WindowStartupLocation="CenterOwner">
	<TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap">
		Welcome to Simple Backup, here is some help to get you started:

- You can do full-backups
- You can include and exclude paths to backup
- You can set versions of backups to keep
- You can keep different configurations for backups
- Once everything is configured you can backup with one command
- All configs are stored in a xml file
	</TextBlock>
</Window>
